Protocol: Venue_Bank_KeyEx

Types: Agent A,B,s;
       Number g,X,Y,Msg;
       Function pk;

Knowledge: 
       A: A,B,s,pk(B),pk(s),g,sk(A,s);
       B: A,B,s,pk(B),inv(pk(B)),pk(s),g,sk(B,s);
       s: A,B,s,pk(s),inv(pk(s)),pk(B),g,sk(B,s),sk(A,s);

Actions:

A->B: {A,B,exp(g,X)}pk(B)
B->s: {| A,B,exp(g,X),exp(g,Y) |}sk(B,s)
s->A: {| A,B,exp(g,X),exp(g,Y) |}sk(A,s)
A->B: {| Msg |}exp(exp(g,X),Y)

Goals:

Msg secret between A,B
B authenticates A on Msg


